{"tid":1738665,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"傳說中的兔子天國: 大久野島","createTime":"2019-11-19T10:12:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T11:46:23.000Z","uid":197098,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f1de76a55a72469db6ae68cda1619baab9e7de91","tid":1738665,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:12:45.000Z","msg":"大家有沒有去過日本「兔仔島」大久野島？這裡有幾千隻自由自在的兔子：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jLnNOtD_sOk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FjLnNOtD_sOk&d=U%2B24RsvDmKluq6DDuV4MqmE7lpprR278wgWha8tNVfY%3D&h=8095e2fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jLnNOtD_sOk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yAoXHKDcW8I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyAoXHKDcW8I&d=U%2B24RsvDmKluq6DDuV4MqmE7lpprR278wgWha8tNVfY%3D&h=86b5cab9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yAoXHKDcW8I</a><br />\n<br />\n但其實島內, 不是每隻兔子都活得開心和長壽，雖然沒有捕食者(predator)威脅，但很多有病, 沒有足夠糧食和營養, 所以兔迷下次去最好帶乾草(Timothy Hay, Oat Hay, Orchard Hay等)和蔬菜🥬。給牠們最基本的高纖維糧食。不要給高糖份和零食, 例如：蘿蔔、水果。<br />\n<br />\n當兔子耳朵平放在後面、耳口向下、坐姿躺下/蹲下就代表牠們不開心，耳朵越後就越憂愁。主人就真的要看看究竟做錯什麼事，牠亦可能生病了:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NdKKWbp7U_k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNdKKWbp7U_k&d=U%2B24RsvDmKluq6DDuV4MqmE7lpprR278wgWha8tNVfY%3D&h=eefac9e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NdKKWbp7U_k</a><br />\n<br />\n憂愁:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0xfQUCe7kp8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0xfQUCe7kp8&d=U%2B24RsvDmKluq6DDuV4MqmE7lpprR278wgWha8tNVfY%3D&h=d22647d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0xfQUCe7kp8</a><br />\n<br />\n這與驚慌(耳朵平放在後面、耳口向側、坐姿蹲下）和憤怒（耳朵和驚慌一樣，但站起來很硬對住你）不同。一個舒適的兔仔會躺下、手腳伸展出來。<br />\n<br />\n兔子因生病(痙攣)而憂愁:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6OYkOlxe8bM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6OYkOlxe8bM&d=U%2B24RsvDmKluq6DDuV4MqmE7lpprR278wgWha8tNVfY%3D&h=684c1fb0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6OYkOlxe8bM</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">資訊來源:</span>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://language.rabbitspeak.com/alas-woe-is-me\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flanguage.rabbitspeak.com%2Falas-woe-is-me&d=U%2B24RsvDmKluq6DDuV4MqmE7lpprR278wgWha8tNVfY%3D&h=c1ad83f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://language.rabbitspeak.com/alas-woe-is-me</a>"},{"pid":"1316c027bdcfa28af29338735f45fc93eaf1f87e","tid":1738665,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:49:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e149cfb76f1ff8b23d50a662bfb65a77ab41d328","tid":1738665,"uid":274136,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T11:46:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">重啟黎明 20/11（三）500am 手足聽朝見<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0gOT6pa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0gOT6pa.png&h=f3ea33dc&s={SIZE}\" /></span></strong></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KfoHZKk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKfoHZKk.png&h=c189493c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">長期戰 不氣餒</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山 各自努力</span>"}]}